window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cole has successfully survived the preschooler exam, and now he’s a full-fledged Scholomance student.</p> <p>More importantly, though, he now has four women bound to him forever.</p> <p>He’s their master, they are his slaves, and they must obey his commands.</p> <p>But his women also gain power and prestige out of the deal, and the Headmistress has taken a special interest in Cole and his coven.</p> <p>Now, they must prove themselves against Scholomance’s enemies: The elder gods and their minions.</p> <p><b>Disclaimer:</b> This novel contains horrific violence, dark rituals, a harem, and deviant mind control sexual escapades.</p>"; 
